OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear
OL,6,Fnight as high cloud moves away. Patchy
OL,7,Flow cloud developing along the south
OL,8,Fcoast of Devon but winds turning
OL,9,Flighter. Staying gusty along coastal
OL,10,Fareas and higher hills.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FWinds stay gusty in places but
OL,13,Feasing during the afternoon, otherwise
OL,14,Fa fine and dry day for all with
OL,15,Flengthy sunshine. Feeling warm away
OL,16,Ffrom the breeze.
